      "text": "Let me explore how this might fit into federated wiki:\n\n> plain text with extendable markup plus named pages with links\n\nI will point to two cases, one where we render text as mathematical expressions but don't evaluate them, the other where we write javascript code and evaluate this in the context of large libraries and visualize the result. Leibnitz would deserve a third approach, but one that would not be out of place among these others.\n\n"
